Name: WORLD  HENTAI
About the game: The WORLD HENTAI is a set of various casual games with luxury girls as a reward. There are classic Tetris and puzzles of any complexity, ranging from 3x3 and ending at 10x10. Enjoy a pleasant pastime solving a puzzle, admiring cute looks and listening to good music. In Game: Cute art works Gallery with pictures from the completed levels. Good music Dynamic Backgrounds Hints in the form of puzzle pieces numbering (can be turned on and off) A lot of puzzle modes - from 3x3 (for beginners) and up to 10x10 (for real pros) Leaderboards Achievements A large number of levels Future: Collectible Cards Everyone wants to get a card with a new game, but it needs your support. The game requires not only your purchases, but also reviews, as well as other activity. In this project, I put a piece of soul and hope that together we can pass the threshold of the test and I will be able to please you with collectible cards.
